%% ============================================================
%% 1. Auth Sequence Diagram
%% ============================================================

---
title: Authentication Flow
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant FastAPI as FastAPI (CPU Service)
    participant Google as Google OAuth
    participant Firestore

    Note over Browser,Firestore: === Login Flow ===
    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /api/auth/login
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Generate CSRF state token
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to Google OAuth<br/>(Set oauth_state cookie)
    Browser->>Google: User authorizes app
    Google-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /api/auth/callback?code=...&state=...

    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /api/auth/callback?code=...&state=...
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Verify oauth_state cookie == state param
    FastAPI->>Google: POST token exchange (auth code → id_token)
    Google-->>FastAPI: {id_token, access_token}
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Decode id_token (no sig verify — trusted exchange)
    FastAPI->>Firestore: upsert_user(google_uid, email, name, avatar)
    Firestore-->>FastAPI: User doc (with role)
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: create_access_token({sub, email, role}) — 15 min<br/>create_refresh_token({sub}) — 7 days
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to frontend<br/>(Set refresh_token httponly cookie,<br/>Delete oauth_state cookie)

    Note over Browser,Firestore: === Page Load / Session Restore ===
    Browser->>FastAPI: POST /api/auth/refresh (refresh_token cookie)
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Decode & verify refresh JWT
    FastAPI->>Firestore: get_user(uid) — fetch fresh role/balance
    Firestore-->>FastAPI: User doc
    FastAPI-->>Browser: {access_token, user: {uid, email, role, token_balance}}
    Browser->>Browser: Store accessToken in memory (JS variable)

    Note over Browser,Firestore: === Authenticated API Call ===
    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /api/jobs (Authorization: Bearer <access_token>)
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: get_current_user(): decode JWT, check type=="access"
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 200 {jobs: [...]}

    Note over Browser,Firestore: === Token Expired (Auto-Refresh) ===
    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /api/jobs (expired access_token)
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
    Browser->>FastAPI: POST /api/auth/refresh (cookie)
    FastAPI-->>Browser: {new access_token, user}
    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /api/jobs (new access_token)
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 200 {jobs: [...]}

    Note over Browser,Firestore: === Logout ===
    Browser->>FastAPI: POST /api/auth/logout
    FastAPI-->>Browser: 200 (Clear refresh_token cookie, max_age=0)
    Browser->>Browser: Clear accessToken & currentUser from memory

