%% ============================================================
%% 3. Job Lifecycle State Diagram
%% ============================================================

---
title: Job Lifecycle
---

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> uploading: POST /api/jobs<br/>(create job doc)

    uploading --> approval: PATCH /api/jobs/{id}<br/>status="approval"<br/>(file upload to GCS complete)

    approval --> processing: POST /api/jobs/{id}/approve<br/>(atomic token deduction,<br/>fires BackgroundTask)

    processing --> done: Background inference completes<br/>(result_uri set)

    processing --> failed: Exception during inference<br/>(error logged)

    done --> [*]
    failed --> [*]

    note right of approval
        GET /api/jobs/{id}/preflight
        returns cost estimate
        (no token deduction)
    end note

    note right of processing
        _run_job_inference() runs in background:
        1. Download GCS file
        2. Run YOLO or SwinUnet
        3. Save result GeoJSON/TIF
        4. Update job status in Firestore
    end note

