%% ============================================================
%% 4. Inference Pipeline (Activity Diagram)
%% ============================================================

---
title: Inference Pipeline
---

flowchart TD
    A[Upload GeoTIFF] --> B{File Size?}
    B -->|"≤25 MB (Free Tier)"| C[Direct multipart upload<br/>POST /api/inference]
    B -->|">25 MB (Commercial)"| D[GCS signed URL upload<br/>POST /api/upload/signed-url]

    D --> E[Browser PUT to GCS]
    E --> F[POST /api/inference/preflight-gcs<br/>Cost estimate]
    F --> G{User confirms cost?}
    G -->|No| Z[Cancel]
    G -->|Yes| H[POST /api/inference/submit]

    C --> I{Backend Selection}
    H --> I

    I -->|"onnxruntime-gpu available"| J[CUDA Provider]
    I -->|"onnxruntime CPU"| K[CPU Provider]
    I -->|"fallback"| L[cv2.dnn]

    J & K & L --> M[Tile GeoTIFF<br/>640x640 overlapping grid]
    M --> N[YOLO inference per tile<br/>NMS filtering]
    N --> O[Pixel to Geo coordinates<br/>using raster transform + GSD]
    O --> P[R-tree spatial dedup<br/>merge detections within min_distance]
    P --> Q[Reproject to WGS84]
    Q --> R[GeoJSON FeatureCollection<br/>with metadata]

    R --> S[Save to results/file_id.geojson]
    S --> T{Commercial?}
    T -->|Yes| U[Atomic token deduction<br/>Firestore transaction]
    T -->|No| V[Mark free trial used]
    U & V --> W[Return result to frontend]
    W --> X[Render on Leaflet map]

